# Copy to .env.local and add your API key for AI maze generation (local / Vercel only).
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_key_here
# OPENAI_API_KEY=your_key_here
#
# Multiplayer (2–10 humans): omit or set false to keep single-player only (default player count = 1).
# NEXT_PUBLIC_MULTIPLAYER_ENABLED=true
#
# itch.io: npm run package:itch → dist/creep-labyrinth-itch.zip (HTML upload).
# CrazyGames: npm run package:crazygames → dist/creep-labyrinth-crazygames.zip (HTML5 upload).
# Static uploads have no API; "Generate with AI" falls back to a random maze.

# itch.io: run `npm run package:itch` — static build has no /api; use Random maze or host with API keys.
